        "username": "paf",
        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2015-03-09 20:48:12.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Code-Review+1\n\nWhoops, looking closer, I see the callback is used from the cancel AST.\n\nLooks good, though I still agree with John that it might be nice to have the group mode called out explicitly.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
